Name: PPSSPP
Description: PPSSPP can run your PSP games on your PC or Android phone in full HD resolution or even higher. It can also upscale textures to make them sharper, and you can enable post-processing shaders to adjust color and brightness the way you like, and other effects.

Name: iSpoofer
Description: If you’re an avid Pokémon Go player, you have probably heard of iSpoofer. iSpoofer is a popular app that allows players to spoof their GPS location in order to catch Pokémon in different parts of the world without leaving the comfort of their own homes.
